Package: btmembers
Title: Import Data on All Members of the Bundestag since 1949
Version: 0.2.5
Date: 2025-12-05
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Philippe",
           family = "Joly",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "philippe.joly@posteo.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4278-9439"))
Description: The Bundestag distributes data on all members of the parliament 
    since 1949 in the form of an XML file (see: 
    <https://www.bundestag.de/services/opendata/>). This  data, however, can be 
    difficult to work with because XML files store information in an arbitrary 
    number of dimensions. btmembers downloads the file "Stammdaten aller 
    Abgeordneten seit 1949 im XML-Format" from the Bundestag website and 
    converts it to either (a) four data frames nested into a list (retaining all 
    the information of the original XML file) or (b) a single, condensed data 
    frame, where the units of analysis are member-terms.
